{"tid":748514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞今夏應當收購沙拿代替美斯","createTime":"2018-07-19T09:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T02:37:24.000Z","uid":43785,"like":18,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cbd938f1fdacb94c3d5ae719f4b1b911147278c6","tid":748514,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"好老實，美斯年事已高。<br />\n呢幾年，甚至係世界杯，都睇到美斯狀態嚴重下跌。<br />\n巴塞連續幾年無力攞歐聯。<br />\n隨住沙維小白尼馬既離開，地上最強已經大不如前。<br />\n<br />\n為應付來年皇馬有夏薩特或麥巴比等球星加入，巴塞今夏應收購沙拿，用一年時間讓佢融入巴塞，讓佢有足夠時間學習及代替美斯的工作。因為每遲一年，巴塞收購人材壓力將會更大。"},{"pid":"9a3c40112f76442f4f9c28ea57ddbef4674109c6","tid":748514,"uid":55335,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"係都Paulo Dybala 啦屌"},{"pid":"c53f51376ab9f922dda96da6c9d5b8d8f5b41901","tid":748514,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"蝕蝕地同你免費交換啦"},{"pid":"8616f52907b924bb7172e672f55c5d890d2cd072","tid":748514,"uid":43785,"like":10,"dislike":6,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c53f51376ab9f922dda96da6c9d5b8d8f5b41901","tid":748514,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:36:10.000Z","msg":"蝕蝕地同你免費交換啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:48:08.000Z","msg":"美斯換條毛咩，過兩年踢中超啦，<br />\n沙拿就一定要買黎頂替佢架啦。"},{"pid":"f304e198687e2f94f22d8754c2b68457505ecdec","tid":748514,"uid":43785,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9a3c40112f76442f4f9c28ea57ddbef4674109c6","tid":748514,"uid":55335,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:32:02.000Z","msg":"係都Paulo Dybala 啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:48:51.000Z","msg":"今年要攞歐聯，下年啦。"},{"pid":"30e0311f5fafcd352f56db894f101bf79eea0879","tid":748514,"uid":41434,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T09:57:53.000Z","msg":"美沙替美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美沙&gt;dybala&gt;沙拿"},{"pid":"7139b67e11763294f64cd063be50523f3